CELL (2, 2): 
Minimum of 1 space per dwelling unit for properties
on blocks with single family zoning, no parking
minimum for all other properties and a maximum of 2
parking spaces per dwelling unit.
Minimum .25 spaces per unit for Multi-Family
Elderly or Disabled.
llm_outputs.rationale: This section provides parking requirements for residential uses in the Transit Supportive Overlay district. However, it does not give a single minimum that applies to all uses, and instead varies based on the specific type of residential property and its location.
